Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.14,0:00:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.25,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.51,0:00:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.06,0:02:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經歷了艱辛生活的拉撒蒂和莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.35,0:02:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是向他們伸出援助之手的瑪魯神父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.23,0:02:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是個把煌珠看作是賺錢工具的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.51,0:02:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕後操縱者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,與酷他們的相遇激發了內心的鬥志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.87,0:02:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉撒蒂和莉莉雅直面這卑劣的陰謀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.18,0:02:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准讓拉撒蒂活著離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.32,0:02:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十二唱 向著自由奔走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.10,0:02:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.49,0:02:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.60,0:02:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守 守護翼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.57,0:02:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開設賭場罪以及破壞社會風氣罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.50,0:02:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加上虐待煌珠罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這座賭鬥場予以查封
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.55,0:02:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要妄想負隅頑抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受法律的懲罰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.92,0:02:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然有守護翼的人混進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.02,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我一併收拾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.35,0:03:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉雅 我們走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.85,0:03:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.40,0:03:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,氣勢洶洶地挑釁他們 有勝算嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.88,0:03:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是守護翼中的精英
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.79,0:03:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有勝算的工作是不會幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.36,0:03:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續射擊 繼續射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.51,0:03:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不賴嘛 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好的預感...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.45,0:03:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開火 連續開火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.44,0:03:59.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這 這可真夠戧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.43,0:04:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.94,0:04:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火力相差太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼能被這些嘍囉幹掉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.00,0:04:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.79,0:04:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然沒子彈了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.95,0:04:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把大家圍起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,風之鎧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.32,0:04:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.36,0:04:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家 快聚在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多虧你了 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.26,0:04:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 也不能一直這麼下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.64,0:04:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再過一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.87,0:04:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再忍耐一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.83,0:04:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我挺不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好困
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.54,0:04:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直戰鬥到現在 這也是難怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.24,0:05:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.46,0:05:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再稍稍堅持一下 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.41,0:05:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 我已經沒力氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們逃不掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.70,0:05:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下就該完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.37,0:05:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼啊 守護翼完全不可靠嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了 立功的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了 陞官和發財
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.34,0:05:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.78,0:05:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是另外一批人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 是我們的夥伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.78,0:05:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像是軍隊一樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.92,0:05:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏已經完全被包圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.72,0:05:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放下武器不許動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休納貝爾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到來的居然是本部的精銳部隊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.03,0:05:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才來晚了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏已經被完全控制住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.09,0:05:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.56,0:06:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那位不是吉漠希司令官嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.92,0:06:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大名倒是如雷貫耳...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.97,0:06:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼終究是贏不了我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.27,0:06:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過是換個地方飼養極品煌珠而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉撒蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今為止承蒙您的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下債款就全部還清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼點還不足以表達感激之情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.65,0:06:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們兩人還有一份大禮要送您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至今為止 真的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就永遠...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.09,0:07:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次見面 吉漠希司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是希絲卡保護官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天勞駕您親臨現場 真是過意不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我自己提出來的話有點那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.96,0:07:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但粉碎規模這麼龐大的黑暗組織的功勞應該不小吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那事等解決了正題後再談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七煌寶樹藏到哪裏去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.59,0:07:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.36,0:07:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.78,0:07:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 七煌寶樹蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.59,0:07:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡保護官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本部的通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.74,0:07:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.80,0:07:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.65,0:07:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,庫魯斯輔佐官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.19,0:07:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 這次實在是...這個...嗯...那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.87,0:07:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之 辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你出色地完成了使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.42,0:07:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.58,0:07:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝您誇獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.19,0:07:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的目標是創建煌珠能幸福生活的環境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這次的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對那個有著巨大的貢獻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.62,0:08:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那份自豪支持著我走到了現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.97,0:08:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼的自豪啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,庫魯斯輔佐官？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.39,0:08:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了本部後 應該還會有更大的任務交給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.35,0:08:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要加油哦 希絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 我會努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.38,0:08:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 這樣就了結一件事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.56,0:08:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要天道存在 邪惡必定消亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡保護官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.92,0:08:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您所報告的賭鬥場老闆...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.57,0:08:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒見到他的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.07,0:08:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.06,0:08:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的身體不可能還能動彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,親信也確確實實地幹掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地下通道的途中出現了塌方 無法前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.91,0:08:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫非...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他什麼人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完成回收了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.36,0:09:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說 你對莉莉雅太念念不忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今後就把你作為素材用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.94,0:09:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瑪魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你了 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.42,0:09:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺你們教會了我們一些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩人要繼續旅程嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.59,0:09:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 因為那是蕾的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.23,0:09:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,努力哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.55,0:09:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷和蕾也一起搭乘好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就距離而言雖然有點繞遠路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.20,0:09:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我覺得搭乘這個能更快到達煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請來這邊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.01,0:10:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.43,0:10:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可沒聽說是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.91,0:10:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的處分先暫緩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.57,0:10:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼樣 最低限度我們會尊重國際協定中所賦予你的權利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.06,0:10:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊 大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.79,0:10:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歪理你就別說了 快把蕾放了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.20,0:10:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希絲卡保護官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.68,0:10:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去說服那個少年...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.30,0:10:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七煌寶樹還有些特殊手續要辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.98,0:10:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 我話還沒說完呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.83,0:10:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 好了 酷也冷靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.79,0:10:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司令官是特種部隊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.92,0:10:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是有些怪異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.23,0:10:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但不用擔心的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.28,0:10:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同意得了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最討厭那種態度的傢伙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.93,0:10:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了本部就能和蕾相見的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼氣勢洶洶地把人帶走了 你要我怎麼相信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為守護翼就是煌珠完全保護協會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.86,0:11:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾也一定會順利地辦完手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.61,0:11:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在七煌寶樹專用的高級床上香香入睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.82,0:11:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼事的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,按下這個按鈕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能取得緊急聯絡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的還能相見的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.52,0:11:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熱戀的兩人就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.46,0:11:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.13,0:12:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是說了守護翼是期盼煌珠幸福的組織了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不會做什麼對你們不利的事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.77,0:12:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 不是還有像賽蕾娜那樣的人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.20,0:12:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.73,0:12:14.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是特殊一例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.37,0:12:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才那些傢伙的帶人方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.03,0:12:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就好像蕾是最大的惡人似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.05,0:12:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那 那是你想得太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是本部精銳部隊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以總是那樣子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.09,0:12:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若是覺得冒犯了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我代為道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.58,0:12:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.54,0:12:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.94,0:12:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.79,0:12:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.11,0:12:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個聲音...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.48,0:13:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直呼喚著我的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.84,0:13:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.64,0:13:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.96,0:13:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.91,0:13:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在等著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.21,0:13:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七煌寶樹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.49,0:13:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.86,0:13:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不需背負那種命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能和那個少年幸福生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.00,0:13:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是個特例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.79,0:13:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是輔佐官一級有資格瞭解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.43,0:13:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 從我的立場出發也有該把握的最低限度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就連那個您都不顧嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是組織的決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.81,0:13:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏有蕾她們的幸福嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.43,0:14:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟煌珠的幸福是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.38,0:14:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的幸福？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.28,0:14:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼啊 突然一下子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.33,0:14:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這裏打盹兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸 幸福...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.49,0:14:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你希望我進來？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.27,0:14:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一 一起洗澡...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.92,0:14:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可 可 可 可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.81,0:14:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很 很窄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然最多該算是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.48,0:14:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但要是碰了不該碰的地方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.92,0:14:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悶在屋裏才胡思亂想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.44,0:15:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是蕾乘的船
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.66,0:15:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.06,0:15:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.22,0:15:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾芙麗·梅札蘭斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.36,0:15:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說你要和那少年去煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.87,0:15:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前路還很漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.45,0:15:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你最好充分瞭解一下自己的身體狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.48,0:15:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是能檢測煌珠身體的設施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不那麼多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.14,0:15:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 趁此機會我們在這船上給你檢測一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.13,0:15:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事 不用麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.11,0:15:52.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經是決定了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.61,0:15:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.18,0:16:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼睜睜地看著被押到守護翼的本部嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.86,0:16:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.57,0:16:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 也許變得有趣起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,著陸之後 就要和那兩人分別了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.21,0:16:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是正好嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既不長也不短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.07,0:16:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不趕快忘記 轉移注意力到下一項任務中去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.90,0:16:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,升級加薪就沒指望了 龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩還真是精神振奮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.93,0:16:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.57,0:16:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護的可是七煌寶樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.38,0:16:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知會拿到多少額外的獎金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.70,0:16:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在已經興奮得心跳加速 口水都要流出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.78,0:17:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我回房間淋浴去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先走一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩可真是優秀啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就一般吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右舷後方有不明飛空艇接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全員進入警戒狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.32,0:17:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全員進入警戒狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.35,0:17:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和闖入我們的空賊艇的船一摸一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是衝著蕾來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.97,0:17:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.84,0:17:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不吸取教訓又來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你們碰蕾一根手指的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.82,0:17:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就作好那種準備來...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.75,0:18:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇 奇雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要有節制啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.05,0:18:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,積蓄下來的飯錢是有限的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.08,0:18:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道 知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說 龍威...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.58,0:18:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼那些傢伙立刻就撤退了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.56,0:18:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是害怕酷了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不太可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.14,0:18:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該不會是因為蕾已經不在那艘船上了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.49,0:18:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.71,0:18:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.61,0:18:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,酷 你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.96,0:18:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.35,0:18:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.32,0:18:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們之所以立即銷聲匿跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.97,0:18:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許是因為偵察之後感覺寡不敵眾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.27,0:19:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到達守護翼本部之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再稍微忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.92,0:19:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直結伴同行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不是不相信你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是有些不好的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.12,0:19:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺再也見不到蕾了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.59,0:19:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.58,0:19:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底什麼時候才到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都已經三天了 三天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別抱怨了 酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.42,0:19:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的只需再忍耐一會兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.78,0:19:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再過一會兒就能見到你心愛的蕾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說什麼愛不愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.91,0:19:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們可真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.75,0:19:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直都在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別使性子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.88,0:19:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不像是男子漢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.46,0:19:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉撒蒂小姐和莉莉雅小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抵達後的居住區分配下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.05,0:19:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.31,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.00,0:20:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下就能保證你們兩人永遠不受任何人干擾地生活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我們一直夢想著的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於在那邊的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.93,0:20:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼問題就問我好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.41,0:20:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們守護翼是煌珠及其同伴的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.69,0:20:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 詳情就到辦公室再談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.68,0:20:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以信賴他們嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.99,0:20:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我到了那邊之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能見到蕾了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.31,0:20:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 能夠看見了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.62,0:20:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.44,0:20:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.58,0:20:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個建築物的地基
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是用飛翔石構成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.69,0:20:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守護翼的科學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.30,0:20:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不只是把飛翔石作為飛空艇的動力源來利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.05,0:21:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是進行著更廣範圍應用的開發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.68,0:21:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害 太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.14,0:22:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在本應充滿希望的地方等待著的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.51,0:22:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤獨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.36,0:22:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疑惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.16,0:22:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及詭行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.16,0:23:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十三唱 守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.12,0:22:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下回 守護翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.44,0:23:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少年的擔心成為了現實

